snippet.title: Super Arter - Trailer
snippet.description:
Recover the Domino Relics stolen by the Dark Wizard, solving the most challenging puzzles, facing enemies, collecting gifts, and discovering the best way for Arter to take the key to the door, in this unique platform/puzzle game.
Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2136060
